citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f63ec02270b062a92d9b17dd1e99d6a013649e","tid":2291593,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca7257c2b2a73ac207ca95ba9dce69fa024bb3d4","tid":2291593,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲用港二技去台灣讀大學兩年<br />\n即係用Asso或者HD讀台灣大學兩年<br />\n呢排應該好多人打算用HF169去移民台灣<br />\n或者台灣當地打工<br />\n<br />\n以前香港未淪陷得咁勁<br />\n好多人都話台灣大學讀完等於冇讀<br />\n仲要好多人話好多野雞大學<br />\n但係依家香港死撚咗<br />\n今年報讀台灣大學應該人數創新高<br />\n<br />\n我想知呢度有冇人對港二技係點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人分享吓經歷係點？<br />\n<br />\n(反正World台係移民台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.....Post呢度冇所謂)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"有fd去左台灣讀"},{"pid":"8b39b440d53d9f0da0661ebe388c3808d19dea1a","tid":2291593,"uid":236155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7ea5a4a2630576c45c2ab53fbf8f3e45a63878c","tid":2291593,"uid":382866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a145353586a5414f0bc32f36266bdad2b8644a","tid":2291593,"uid":382612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:02:53.000Z","msg":"如果係香港讀完u （非三大）去台灣讀master, aim移民，可以點做？係咪讀完喺嗰邊做一年野就可以有永久居留權？唔係太清楚，希望有人解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:46:52.000Z","msg":"在台灣畢業後，合約不間斷咁做五年野，可以拎定居&mdash;&gt;換身份證（HF168)<br />\n或者畢業後返香港做2年，可以申請台灣的居留證&mdash;&gt;移民監一年（做唔做野都得）&mdash;&gt;定居證&mdash;&gt;身份證(HF169)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.teco-hk.org/cp.aspx?n=23B1A3A6BA521F00&amp;s=F60360B41EF2C6D2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teco-hk.org%2Fcp.aspx%3Fn%3D23B1A3A6BA521F00%26s%3DF60360B41EF2C6D2&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5iVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=b6c4460a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.teco-hk.org/cp.aspx?n=23B1A3A6BA521F00&amp;s=F603